Title: Unforgottable Mayodiya,Roing &amp; Pasighat
DateModified: '2019-03-03'
DatePublished: '2019-03-03'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/unforgottable-mayodiya-roing-pasighat
SetInCountry: India
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Pragyan  Dutta
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "It was one of my latest unforgottable trip to Mayodiya/Roing and Pasighat,Arunachal\
  \ Pradesh,India.\nTasting many more local food like Boil Chicken with local vegetable,Boiled\
  \ Pork with bambooshoot etc.\nWe travelled from Guwahati the Capital of Assam,India\
  \ by car.\nFirst day we stayed at Roing.The naturalview from our resort was soo\
  \ soothing.A cold hilly wind kissed us the whole day.The sound of Nature,birds are\
  \ awesome.\nThen we head towards mayodiya,getting so much snow fall.It feels like\
  \ heaven.\nSome traditional food was also tested which the local people boiled in\
  \ a beer Can(Chicken with smoked tomatoes with green chilly boil)\nOn the next day\
  \ we head towards Pasighat.\nIts an another world.The Siang river surrounded by\
  \ the green hill station,white sands of the river.Orange trees on the river bank.Orange\
  \ ball at the fresh greenary.\nThe fresh air night time with a glass of whisky it\
  \ was feeling awesome.\nAfter all it was an amazing experience for me when i was\
  \ in Arunachal Pradesh,India.\n\nI can guide the full trip if any one comes for\
  \ mayodiya,roing and pasighat.\n\n\nPragyan Dutta\n9706381992\n[email\_protected]\n\
  Guwahati,Assam,India.\n\nwww.elysiancommunications.in"
